(2, 1, 'In 21st-century Korea, shamanism is not only thriving — but evolving', 'agriculture-farming', 'In 21st-century Korea, shamanism is not only thriving — but evolving', 'In 21st-century Korea, shamanism is not only thriving — but evolving', NULL, NULL, '1728645974.webp', 'In 21st-century Korea, shamanism is not only thriving — but evolving', 'In 21st-century Korea, shamanism is not only thriving — but evolving', 'In 21st-century Korea, shamanism is not only thriving — but evolving', 1, 1, 1, '1', 1, '2024-10-09 01:09:43', '2024-10-11 05:56:14'),
(4, 1, 'Listening Without Prejudice', 'listening-without-prejudice', '“Don’t go there. It’s squalid, filled with filth and toxic waste.” I get cautioned. “When radioactive material enters the body, it can travel to different locations, such as the bone marrow, where it will continue to emit radiation until it is either removed or decays.”', 'zxv', NULL, NULL, 'default-image.jpg', 'Teletype', 'Teletype', 'Teletype', 0, 0, 0, '1', 1, '2024-10-09 03:35:51', '2024-10-14 00:45:51'),
(5, 1, '10 Intelligent Health Gadgets You Can’t Live Without in 2024 (That Actually Work!)', '10-intelligent-health-gadgets-you-cant-live-without-in-2024-that-actually-work', '10 Intelligent Health Gadgets You Can’t Live Without in 2024 (That Actually Work!)', '<h1 id=\"07be\" class=\"pw-post-title yj wb ye bf nu yk aqp sz yl ym yn aqq ta yo yp jo aqr aqs jp jq jr aqt aqu js jt ju aqv aqw jv jw bk\" data-testid=\"storyTitle\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">10 Intelligent Health Gadgets You Can’t Live Without in 2024 (That Actually Work!)</h1><p></p>', NULL, NULL, 'upload/post/default-image.jpg', '10 Intelligent Health Gadgets You Can’t Live Without in 2024 (That Actually Work!)', '10 Intelligent Health Gadgets You Can’t Live Without in 2024 (That Actually Work!)', '10 Intelligent Health Gadgets You Can’t Live Without in 2024 (That Actually Work!)', 0, 1, 1, '1', 1, '2024-10-09 06:12:25', '2024-10-11 05:17:50'),
(6, 1, 'Back in my 20s and 30s, I could pretty much ingest anything I wanted and probably lose weight if I did any exercise whatsoever.', 'back-in-my-20s-and-30s-i-could-pretty-much-ingest-anything-i-wanted-and-probably-lose-weight-if-i-did-any-exercise-whatsoever', 'Back in my 20s and 30s, I could pretty much ingest anything I wanted and probably lose weight if I did any exercise whatsoever.', '<p id=\"4d91\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph aej aek ye ael b ys aem aen aeo yu aep aeq aer nz aes aet aeu od aev aew aex oh aey aez afa afb nl bk\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">Ah, to have a young person’s metabolism, eh?</p><p id=\"e0c2\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph aej aek ye ael b ys aem aen aeo yu aep aeq aer nz aes aet aeu od aev aew aex oh aey aez afa afb nl bk\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">Back in my 20s and 30s, I could pretty much ingest anything I wanted and probably <em class=\"afl\">lose </em>weight if I did any exercise whatsoever.</p><p id=\"e8d5\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph aej aek ye ael b ys aem aen aeo yu aep aeq aer nz aes aet aeu od aev aew aex oh aey aez afa afb nl bk\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\"><strong class=\"ael nu\">Nowadays? That’s gonna be a big “lol” from me.</strong></p><p id=\"3b8e\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph aej aek ye ael b ys aem aen aeo yu aep aeq aer nz aes aet aeu od aev aew aex oh aey aez afa afb nl bk\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">Take last week, for example.</p><p id=\"3ffd\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph aej aek ye ael b ys aem aen aeo yu aep aeq aer nz aes aet aeu od aev aew aex oh aey aez afa afb nl bk\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\"><mark class=\"aui akc ao\">I don’t eat a lot of sugar.</mark></p><p id=\"e6c8\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph aej aek ye ael b ys aem aen aeo yu aep aeq aer nz aes aet aeu od aev aew aex oh aey aez afa afb nl bk\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">In fact, I would almost <em class=\"afl\">never </em>eat sugar if it wasn’t in the house.</p><p id=\"e286\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph aej aek ye ael b ys aem aen aeo yu aep aeq aer nz aes aet aeu od aev aew aex oh aey aez afa afb nl bk\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">But recently my wife and younger son (who inherited <em class=\"afl\">her </em>sweet tooth) decided it would be a good idea to buy a freezer cake and some ice cream on a random Tuesday night as a treat.</p><p id=\"8526\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph aej aek ye ael b ys aem aen aeo yu aep aeq aer nz aes aet aeu od aev aew aex oh aey aez afa afb nl bk\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">Now I may have zero desire to eat sugar on a day-to-day basis, but for some weird reason, I <strong class=\"ael nu\">MUST </strong>eat if it’s in the house.</p><p id=\"60de\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph aej aek ye ael b ys aem aen aeo yu aep aeq aer nz aes aet aeu od aev aew aex oh aey aez afa afb nl bk\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\"><strong class=\"ael nu\">So for a couple of nights until it was all gone, I gorged.</strong></p><p id=\"70fb\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph aej aek ye ael b ys aem aen aeo yu aep aeq aer nz aes aet aeu od aev aew aex oh aey aez afa afb nl bk\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">And that’s all it takes at this age, I’m afraid.</p><p id=\"1448\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph aej aek ye ael b ys aem aen aeo yu aep aeq aer nz aes aet aeu od aev aew aex oh aey aez afa afb nl bk\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">On the third morning, I woke up feeling shameful and fat as s**t.</p><p id=\"076f\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph aej aek ye ael b ys aem aen aeo yu aep aeq aer nz aes aet aeu od aev aew aex oh aey aez afa afb nl bk\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">So\r\n now imagine ingesting something that’s not only filled with useless, \r\nempty calories but has also been proven to wreck your ability to work \r\nthose calories off.</p><p id=\"ba3e\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph aej aek ye ael b ys aem aen aeo yu aep aeq aer nz aes aet aeu od aev aew aex oh aey aez afa afb nl bk\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">Let’s talk about that real quick.</p><figure class=\"adw adx ady adz aea adv aee aef paragraph-image\"><div role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"aqy aqz gh ara bh arb\"><div class=\"aee aef aug\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\"><source data-testid=\"og\"><img alt=\"Imagine spending hours in the gym every week only to sabotage your own efforts. I used to do it all the time.\" class=\"bh te aeb c\" width=\"700\" height=\"468\" src=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:700/1*g0fpXC7yW3kpcreXJ_xaZw.jpeg\"></picture></div></div><figcaption class=\"aec jg aed aee aef aeg aeh bf b bg z gb\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">Imagine\r\n spending hours in the gym every week only to sabotage your own efforts \r\nbefore you see the results? I used to do it all the time. (Licensed by \r\nthe author under the <a class=\"af aei\" href=\"https://unsplash.com/plus/license\" rel=\"noopener ugc nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Unsplash+ License</a>)</figcaption></figure><h2 id=\"c1a6\" class=\"arp arg ye bf arh tn arq io kx tp arr ir la nz ars iu oc od art ix og oh aru ja ok yh bk\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">The worst diet decision you…</h2><div class=\"ab cc\"><div class=\"cj bh vf xj xk xl\"><div class=\"akj akk bh l gh akl\"></div><div class=\"l c\"><div class=\"akm akn l ako\"><div class=\"ab cc jg akp\"><div class=\"akq akr aks akt aku bp ph te ab db jg\"><h2 class=\"akv b ji aen akw jl aeq akx aky aet akz ala aew alb alc aez ald ale alf\">P, read this story from James Julian — and all the best stories on Medium.</h2><div class=\"ph l\"><p class=\"bf b bg z bk\">The\r\n author made this story available to Medium members only. \r\nUpgrade to instantly unlock this story plus other member-only benefits.</p></div><div class=\"alg l\"><div class=\"tm ab q akf\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" class=\"aki bo add do\"></svg></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"tm ab q akf\"><p class=\"bf b bg z 